===== Involved rules descriptions:

[iamf][Rule #0] id: assert-obu-trimming-rules
Section 3.2
OBU trimming checks:
- When num_samples_to_trim_at_start is non-zero, all preceding Audio Frame OBUs with the same audio_substream_id SHALL have their num_samples_to_trim_at_start field equal to num_samples_per_frame.
- The sum of num_samples_to_trim_at_start and num_samples_to_trim_at_end SHALL be less than or equal to num_samples_per_frame.

